AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; I would say that is 25 out of 26. I think the letter B kind of looks like V. &gt;&gt; A B. &gt;&gt; Now, you don\'t have to use realistic avatars like this. You can use animated characters such as this guy here with the surprised emotion.'

[06:03] [scene:talk]
