AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; I came in 2 hours early only to find that someone had eaten all the pizza. &gt;&gt; Say it isn\'t. So, one more quick Avatar X example. Then I want to show you something else here that is pretty cool. Now, this is just with the neutral'

